\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n事關老母未出過國，女友又想去澳洲<br />\n<br />\n屌噉冇理由去兩次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n痴線，呢個已經係理由做兩次，你呢個計劃係自殺行為。"},{"pid":"636ea19cf9b2afd44505eee0f809b4b06769c7ed","tid":433850,"uid":36363,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-13T06:05:04.000Z","msg":"你老母有無家姐細妹/唔八婆既朋友？<br />\n你求其搵個親戚陪你老母都唔好呢個組合 真自殺行為<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"577b17575596965d8de2790264392e3fcb27b761","tid":433850,"uid":105302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-13T06:11:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>應該叫埋你老豆去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n到底係有幾睇唔開先會咁既組合去旅行<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"013f0154076c2c07f09a7777d15bf2af74d5d831","tid":433850,"uid":105302,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-13T06:14:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>好撚出事既組合<br />\n都唔知點解你會有個咁既idea<br />\nBtw樓上話apartment係最好既選擇</blockquote><br />\nGood idea <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n事關老母未出過國，女友又想去澳洲<br />\n<br />\n屌噉冇理由去兩次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n痴線，呢個已經係理由做兩次，你呢個計劃係自殺行為。</blockquote><br />\n老母未出過國既話其實你之後帶佢去日本佢應該仲開心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n日本近近地，多野食多野買多景睇，啱晒d師奶仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n利申唔係崇日撚，只係老母去澳洲唔會悶咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1a234d9fe22adac7a729707a42eb3f00c868e834","tid":433850,"uid":6604,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-13T06:53:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>好撚出事既組合<br />\n都唔知點解你會有個咁既idea<br />\nBtw樓上話apartment係最好既選擇</blockquote><br />\nGood idea <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n事關老母未出過國，女友又想去澳洲<br />\n<br />\n屌噉冇理由去兩次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n同老母去東南亞咪算囉<br />\n澳洲真係唔啱老人家<br />\n除非係去探親"},{"pid":"b740150ab810fcf696f6c79a885068ff02347c75","tid":433850,"uid":82997,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-13T07:01:12.000Z","msg":"同樓主你情況一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n最後我同男友一間房 佢媽自己一間（加錢都咁話）<br />\n雖然我同佢媽平時無乜野 但要同一間房既話真係好kick手... 唔通三條友爭廁所咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 同男朋友都無得二人世界啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我自己覺得同親屋企人/長輩旅行，最好跟團... <br />\n因為我知自由行實死梗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 大家想去既野、想食既野唔同。好易搞到心中有刺/嘈交... 身為後輩又唔好意思反面，但又唔係幾想妥協，最黎要男朋友做中間人就煩。<br />\n跟團就乜都由導遊決定，煩惱已經少好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但樓主你澳洲應該唔會跟旅行團啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 祝你好運"},{"pid":"7a557543ee5d66b78966480dbd422632f0c9516e","tid":433850,"uid":153168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-13T07:09:43.000Z","msg":"3p <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}